Package: ReproFlow
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Reproducibility Framework for R Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Abu", "Saadat", email = "saadatabu1996@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive reproducibility framework that automatically captures
    the entire analysis environment including R session info, package versions,
    data provenance, parameter choices, and random seeds. Generates executable
    scripts with Docker and renv configurations to ensure complete reproducibility
    of research workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    renv,
    jsonlite,
    digest,
    yaml,
    cli,
    rlang
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
